# Skills: real files live in .agents/skills (tracked, tool-agnostic).
# .claude/skills holds local junctions/symlinks back to them — git can't
# represent junctions, so it would double-track the files. Ignore the mirror;
# the installer/junctions regenerate it locally.
.claude/skills/
